  "prompt": "What is a suitable solar panel installation provider near Somis, California CA?",
  "response": "While I can't access real-time data, I can suggest some strategies to find suitable solar panel installation providers near Somis, California:\n\n1. **Online Directories**: Websites like EnergySage, SolarReviews, and Yelp can help you find local solar installation companies with user reviews and ratings.\n\n2. **Local Searches**: Conduct a Google search for \u201csolar panel installation near Somis, CA\u201d to find providers in your area.\n\n3. **Local Utilities**: Check with your local utility company, as they often have partnerships or recommendations for solar providers.\n\n4. **Community Recommendations**: Ask neighbors or community groups in Somis for their recommendations based on their experiences.\n\n5. **Certifications and Affiliations**: Look for companies that are certified by the North American Board of Certified Energy Practitioners (NABCEP) or members of the Solar Energy Industries Association (SEIA).\n\nWhen selecting a provider, consider factors like experience, warranties, financing options, and customer service. Make sure to get multiple quotes and review the proposals carefully before making a decision.",
